\/\/achaumedia.vn\/kinh-nghiem-chup-anh-ngoai-canh.html\/#Kinh_nghiem_chup_anh_ngoai_canh_cho_cac_cap_doi\" title=\"Kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh cho c\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i\">Kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh cho c\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/kinh-nghiem-chup-anh-ngoai-canh.html\/#Co_dau_chu_re_nen_chon_boi_canh_yeu_thich\" title=\"C\u00f4 d\u00e2u, ch\u00fa r\u1ec3 n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh y\u00eau th\u00edch\">C\u00f4 d\u00e2u, ch\u00fa r\u1ec3 n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh y\u00eau th\u00edch<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/kinh-nghiem-chup-anh-ngoai-canh.html\/#Can_sap_xep_thoi_gian_hop_ly\" title=\"C\u1ea7n s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp th\u1eddi gian h\u1ee3p l\u00fd\">C\u1ea7n s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp th\u1eddi gian h\u1ee3p l\u00fd<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/kinh-nghiem-chup-anh-ngoai-canh.html\/#Khong_nen_bo_qua_nhung_boi_canh_quen_thuoc_don_gian\" title=\"Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean b\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh quen thu\u1ed9c, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n\">Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean b\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh quen thu\u1ed9c, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/kinh-nghiem-chup-anh-ngoai-canh.html\/#Co_dau_khong_nen_chon_qua_nhieu_bo_trang_phuc_hay_doi_kieu_trang_diem_lien_tuc\" title=\"C\u00f4 d\u00e2u kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ed9 trang ph\u1ee5c hay \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u trang \u0111i\u1ec3m li\u00ean t\u1ee5c\">C\u00f4 d\u00e2u kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ed9 trang ph\u1ee5c hay \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u trang \u0111i\u1ec3m li\u00ean t\u1ee5c<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/kinh-nghiem-chup-anh-ngoai-canh.html\/#Nen_tin_tuong_vao_nhiep_anh_gia_ban_da_lua_chon\" title=\"N\u00ean tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh gia b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn\">N\u00ean tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh gia b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/kinh-nghiem-chup-anh-ngoai-canh.html\/#Kinh_nghiem_chup_anh_ngoai_canh_Tao_dang_chup_hinh\" title=\"Kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh: T\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh\u00a0\">Kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh: T\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh\u00a0<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/kinh-nghiem-chup-anh-ngoai-canh.html\/#Tay_trong_tay_cung_nhau_di_khap_the_gian\" title=\"Tay trong tay c\u00f9ng nhau \u0111i kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gian\">Tay trong tay c\u00f9ng nhau \u0111i kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gian<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/kinh-nghiem-chup-anh-ngoai-canh.html\/#Ruot_duoi_nhau\" title=\"R\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i nhau\">R\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i nhau<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/kinh-nghiem-chup-anh-ngoai-canh.html\/#Tua_lung_vao_nhau\" title=\"T\u1ef1a l\u01b0ng v\u00e0o nhau\">T\u1ef1a l\u01b0ng v\u00e0o nhau<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/kinh-nghiem-chup-anh-ngoai-canh.html\/#Om_nhau_cuoi_rang_ro\" title=\"\u00d4m nhau, c\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1\">\u00d4m nhau, c\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-12\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/kinh-nghiem-chup-anh-ngoai-canh.html\/#Dung_canh_nhau_nhin_ve_mot_huong\" title=\"\u0110\u1ee9ng c\u1ea1nh nhau nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t h\u01b0\u1edbng\">\u0110\u1ee9ng c\u1ea1nh nhau nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t h\u01b0\u1edbng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-13\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/kinh-nghiem-chup-anh-ngoai-canh.html\/#Quang_vai_kieng_chan_hon_chang\" title=\"Qu\u00e0ng vai, ki\u1ec5ng ch\u00e2n h\u00f4n ch\u00e0ng\">Qu\u00e0ng vai, ki\u1ec5ng ch\u00e2n h\u00f4n ch\u00e0ng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-14\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/kinh-nghiem-chup-anh-ngoai-canh.html\/#Om_tu_phia_sau\" title=\"\u00d4m t\u1eeb ph\u00eda sau\">\u00d4m t\u1eeb ph\u00eda sau<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-15\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/kinh-nghiem-chup-anh-ngoai-canh.html\/#Cham_cam_co_dau\" title=\"Ch\u1ea1m\u00a0c\u1eb1m c\u00f4 d\u00e2u\">Ch\u1ea1m\u00a0c\u1eb1m c\u00f4 d\u00e2u<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-16\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/kinh-nghiem-chup-anh-ngoai-canh.html\/#Choc_gheo_nhau\" title=\"Ch\u1ecdc gh\u1eb9o nhau\">Ch\u1ecdc gh\u1eb9o nhau<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-17\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/kinh-nghiem-chup-anh-ngoai-canh.html\/#Nu_hon_tren_tay\" title=\"N\u1ee5 h\u00f4n tr\u00ean tay\">N\u1ee5 h\u00f4n tr\u00ean tay<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-18\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/kinh-nghiem-chup-anh-ngoai-canh.html\/#Nhay_cung_nhau\" title=\"Nh\u1ea3y c\u00f9ng nhau\">Nh\u1ea3y c\u00f9ng nhau<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-19\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/kinh-nghiem-chup-anh-ngoai-canh.html\/#Cong_nang_tren_lung\" title=\"C\u00f5ng n\u00e0ng tr\u00ean l\u01b0ng\">C\u00f5ng n\u00e0ng tr\u00ean l\u01b0ng<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><em>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u1eefng g\u00ec khi ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh c\u01b0\u1edbi ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media xem qua m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i<strong> kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh<\/strong> cho c\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i s\u1eafp c\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 album \u1ea3nh c\u01b0\u1edbi ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o nh\u00e9!<\/em><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-9725\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/chup-hinh-cuoi-ngoai-canh-ft-1-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"Kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh c\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb9p\" width=\"851\" height=\"638\" \/><\/p>\n<h2 class=\"titView\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Kinh_nghiem_chup_anh_ngoai_canh_cho_cac_cap_doi\"><\/span><strong>Kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh cho c\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<div class=\"showText fr-view\">\n<p>C\u00e1c c\u00f4 d\u00e2u, ch\u00fa r\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111a ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ee1 ng\u1ee1 khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n album \u1ea3nh c\u01b0\u1edbi. V\u00ec th\u1ebf h\u00f4m nay ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chia s\u1ebb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u01b0u \u00fd quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2m l\u00fd tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean nh\u1ea5t khi \u0111i\u00a0<strong>ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh c\u01b0\u1edbi ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Co_dau_chu_re_nen_chon_boi_canh_yeu_thich\"><\/span><strong>C\u00f4 d\u00e2u, ch\u00fa r\u1ec3 n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh y\u00eau th\u00edch<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>N\u01a1i ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh c\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m, l\u00e0 v\u00f9ng bi\u1ec3n xanh hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1eb1ng ao \u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi ho\u1eb7c ngay nh\u1eefng g\u00f3c ph\u1ed1 th\u00e2n quen. Ch\u1ec9 khi ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh \u1edf n\u01a1i m\u00ecnh y\u00eau th\u00edch, uy\u00ean \u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng, ngo\u00e0i ra hai b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung c\u1ea3nh khi l\u00ean h\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 m\u00ecnh mong \u0111\u1ee3i.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-9621\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/phimtruongalibaba-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh\" width=\"851\" height=\"567\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Can_sap_xep_thoi_gian_hop_ly\"><\/span><strong>C\u1ea7n s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp th\u1eddi gian h\u1ee3p l\u00fd<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 cho b\u1ed9 \u1ea3nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y. C\u00f4 d\u00e2u, ch\u00fa r\u1ec3 n\u00ean s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp sao cho bu\u1ed5i ch\u1ee5p b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00fac \u00e1nh b\u00ecnh minh, k\u1ecbp b\u1eaft nh\u1eefng tia n\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u00e0y v\u1eeba lung linh t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng. T\u1edbi tr\u01b0a, c\u1ea3 hai n\u00ean ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, tr\u00e1nh tr\u01b0a n\u1eafng g\u1eaft, \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ec1u m\u00e1t m\u1edbi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n l\u1ea5y \u00e1nh ho\u00e0ng h\u00f4n r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Khong_nen_bo_qua_nhung_boi_canh_quen_thuoc_don_gian\"><\/span><strong>Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean b\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh quen thu\u1ed9c, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Khi nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp uy\u00ean \u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0o b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean lo s\u1ee3 c\u1ea3nh s\u1eafc k\u00e9m \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc. V\u00ec th\u00f4ng qua con m\u1eaft chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p m\u00e1y \u1ea3nh, \u1ed1ng k\u00ednh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p th\u00ec nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3nh v\u1eadt t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean lung linh s\u1eafc m\u00e0u trong \u1ea3nh. \u1ede m\u1ed7i b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh, \u0111i\u1ec1u uy\u00ean \u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00ean quan t\u00e2m l\u00e0 ch\u0103m ch\u00fa bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea1t c\u1ea3m x\u00fac sao cho t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, ch\u00e2n th\u1ef1c.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Co_dau_khong_nen_chon_qua_nhieu_bo_trang_phuc_hay_doi_kieu_trang_diem_lien_tuc\"><\/span><strong>C\u00f4 d\u00e2u kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ed9 trang ph\u1ee5c hay \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u trang \u0111i\u1ec3m li\u00ean t\u1ee5c<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap c\u00f4 d\u00e2u c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian t\u1eadp trung cho vi\u1ec7c\u00a0<strong>ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh c\u01b0\u1edbi ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh<\/strong>, nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian n\u1eafm b\u1eaft nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u1eb9p cho m\u1ed7i b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh c\u01b0\u1edbi. N\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ch\u1ee5c ph\u00fac, c\u00f4 d\u00e2u l\u1ea1i lo chuy\u1ec7n thay v\u00e1y \u00e1o, \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e0u m\u00f4i, m\u00e0u m\u1eaft, ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c m\u1edbi\u2026 th\u00ec s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian. B\u1ed9 \u1ea3nh c\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1eb9p khi c\u00f4 d\u00e2u, ch\u00fa r\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian b\u00ean nhau v\u00e0 h\u00e0i h\u00f2a v\u1edbi khung c\u1ea3nh t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-9622\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/phim-truong-Lamour-4.jpg.pagespeed.ce_.TP68c9NJp8-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"Ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh c\u01b0\u1edbi trong phim tr\u01b0\u1eddng\" width=\"851\" height=\"566\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nen_tin_tuong_vao_nhiep_anh_gia_ban_da_lua_chon\"><\/span><strong>N\u00ean tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh gia b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n album c\u01b0\u1edbi, c\u00f4 d\u00e2u v\u00e0 ch\u00fa r\u1ec3 n\u00ean tham kh\u1ea3o t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m <strong>ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh<\/strong>, g\u1eb7p tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u k\u1ef9 phong c\u00e1ch, tay ngh\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh gia m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn. Uy\u00ean \u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n th\u00e2n m\u1eadt, chia s\u1ebb tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n mong \u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ee5p hi\u1ec3u, n\u1eafm b\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00fd th\u00edch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dia-diem-chup-anh-dep-o-da-lat-ly-tuong-nhat.html\/\">\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh c\u01b0\u1edbi ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t\u00a0<\/a><\/p>\n<div class=\"main-article__video-block\">\n<div class=\"player-item\">\n<h2 class=\"player-item__inner\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Kinh_nghiem_chup_anh_ngoai_canh_Tao_dang_chup_hinh\"><\/span><strong>Kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh: T\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"abody\" class=\"main-article__content\">\n<p>Khi\u00a0ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh c\u01b0\u1edbi\u00a0vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u201cth\u00e0nh ph\u1ea9m\u201d c\u1ee7a b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh. H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00f4 d\u00e2u ch\u00fa r\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00f9ng khi \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ed1ng k\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh c\u01b0\u1edbi l\u1ebd ra \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t l\u1ea1i tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f4 c\u1ee9ng, nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n.B\u1ea1n \u0111\u1eebng lo l\u1eafng, ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i b\u00ed quy\u1ebft\u00a0t\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh sau s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c album \u1ea3nh \u0111a d\u1ea1ng, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n \u0111i\u1ec7u.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tay_trong_tay_cung_nhau_di_khap_the_gian\"><\/span><strong>Tay trong tay c\u00f9ng nhau \u0111i kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gian<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>V\u1edbi c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh n\u00e0y, hai b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n di\u1ec5n \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u1ea3. H\u00e3y n\u1eafm tay nhau v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u00e0y v\u1eabn nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. Ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0, h\u00f4m nay hai b\u1ea1n m\u1eb7c tr\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ed9 trang ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n, trang \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u1ef9 h\u01a1n v\u00e0 thay m\u00e1y \u1ea3nh \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng m\u00e1y ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh \u201cx\u1ecbn\u201d.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1eebng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ebfp\u00a0 \u1ea3nh gia, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 kh\u1eafc bi\u1ebft \u201dch\u1ed9p\u201d l\u1ea1i kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc ng\u1ecdt ng\u00e0o nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a hai b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-9628\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/chup-anh-cuoi-kiue-co-dien-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"Ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh c\u01b0\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n\" width=\"851\" height=\"568\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ruot_duoi_nhau\"><\/span><strong>R\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i nhau<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>H\u00e3y \u0111u\u1ed5i theo n\u00e0ng, b\u1eaft l\u1ea5y v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e0ng r\u1eddi xa v\u00f2ng tay. Nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh gia s\u1ebd l\u01b0u l\u1ea1i kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc ng\u1ecdt ng\u00e0o, l\u00e3ng m\u1ea1n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a hai b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tua_lung_vao_nhau\"><\/span><strong>T\u1ef1a l\u01b0ng v\u00e0o nhau<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>T\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng h\u00f4n nh\u00e2n h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac, b\u00ecnh y\u00ean ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u00f4 d\u00e2u v\u00e0 ch\u00fa r\u1ec3 t\u1ef1a l\u01b0ng v\u00e0o nhau b\u00ecnh y\u00ean, m\u1eb7c cho c\u1ea3m x\u00fac l\u1ea1c tr\u00f4i. Ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n g\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00e9p hay c\u1ed1 g\u1ed3ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 di\u1ec5n, c\u1ea3m x\u00fac th\u1eadt s\u1ebd to\u00e1t l\u00ean ngay trong t\u1eebng h\u01a1i th\u1edf c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Om_nhau_cuoi_rang_ro\"><\/span><strong>\u00d4m nhau, c\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>T\u01b0 th\u1ebf ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh c\u01b0\u1edbi\u00a0n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u00f4i uy\u00ean \u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh l\u00e3ng m\u1ea1n. \u00c1nh m\u1eaft l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t khi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd r\u1eb1ng \u00f4m l\u1ea5y nhau v\u00e0 c\u01b0\u1eddi t\u01b0\u01a1i r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1\u00a0th\u1eadt\u00a0\u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n? Ch\u1ee5p\u00a0\u1ea3nh c\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eadt ra c\u0169ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ea5y!<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dung_canh_nhau_nhin_ve_mot_huong\"><\/span><strong>\u0110\u1ee9ng c\u1ea1nh nhau nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t h\u01b0\u1edbng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_444012\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\">\n<p class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u00fang ta h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng nhau h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0 d\u1ef1ng x\u00e2y n\u00f3<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o \u1ed1ng k\u00ednh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p, c\u1ea3 hai c\u00f9ng nhau nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u01b0 l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh cho s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft b\u00ean nhau tr\u1ecdn \u0111\u1eddi.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-9627\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/phong-cach-chup-anh-cuoi-13.jpg.pagespeed.ce_.hd4NKc_5ai-300x190.jpg\" alt=\"kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh\" width=\"851\" height=\"539\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Quang_vai_kieng_chan_hon_chang\"><\/span><strong>Qu\u00e0ng vai, ki\u1ec5ng ch\u00e2n h\u00f4n ch\u00e0ng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Tr\u00f4ng b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd th\u1eadt nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 khi ki\u1ec5ng ch\u00e2n l\u00ean \u00f4m l\u1ea5y ch\u00e0ng v\u00e0 h\u00f4n. Phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong c\u00e1c ki\u1ec3u ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p, \u0111\u00e1ng y\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4 d\u00e2u y\u00eau th\u00edch.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Om_tu_phia_sau\"><\/span><strong>\u00d4m t\u1eeb ph\u00eda sau<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_443972\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\">\n<p class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1i \u00f4m t\u1eeb ph\u00eda sau gi\u00fap ch\u00e0ng c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn r\u00f5 h\u01a1n t\u00ecnh y\u00eau n\u00e0ng d\u00e0nh trao<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p>H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ch\u00fa r\u1ec3 \u00f4m l\u1ea5y c\u00f4 d\u00e2u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda sau \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 quen thu\u1ed9c. N\u00e0ng h\u00e3y l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, h\u00e3y \u00f4m l\u1ea5y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1eeb ph\u00eda sau th\u1eadt ch\u1eadt. Ch\u00e0ng c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng, ch\u0103m s\u00f3c. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ki\u1ec3u ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n cho c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cham_cam_co_dau\"><\/span><strong>Ch\u1ea1m\u00a0c\u1eb1m c\u00f4 d\u00e2u<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>M\u1ed9t ki\u1ec3u ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh ng\u1ecdt ng\u00e0o kh\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng l\u00e0 ch\u00fa r\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng tay ch\u1ea1m c\u1eb1m c\u1ee7a c\u00f4 d\u00e2u m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch h\u1edd h\u1eefng, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u1ed9t n\u1ee5 h\u00f4n n\u1ed3ng ch\u00e1y.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Choc_gheo_nhau\"><\/span><strong>Ch\u1ecdc gh\u1eb9o nhau<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>H\u00ecnh c\u01b0\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng nghi\u00eam t\u00fac, kh\u00f4 khan. M\u1ed9t ch\u00fat b\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f9a, tr\u00eau gh\u1eb9o nhau s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ng\u1ecdt ng\u00e0o. Hai b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y c\u1ee9 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i vui \u0111\u00f9a c\u00f9ng nhau v\u00e0 qu\u00ean \u1ed1ng k\u00ednh \u0111i!<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_444022\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\">\n<p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i \u00f4m nhau hay h\u00f4n nhau, \u00e1nh m\u1eaft c\u01b0\u1eddi, c\u00e1i kho\u00e1c tay c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u1ee9ng minh t\u00ecnh y\u00eau ng\u1ecdt ng\u00e0o.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nu_hon_tren_tay\"><\/span><strong>N\u1ee5 h\u00f4n tr\u00ean tay<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Trao cho n\u00e0ng m\u1ed9t n\u1ee5 h\u00f4n tr\u00ean tay nh\u01b0 l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng m\u00ecnh g\u1eafn b\u00f3 su\u1ed1t qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u1eddi c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nhay_cung_nhau\"><\/span><strong>Nh\u1ea3y c\u00f9ng nhau<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Cho d\u00f9 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng xoay \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n hay m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec7u nh\u1ea3y theo phong c\u00e1ch khi\u00eau v\u0169, nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh v\u1edbi ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng n\u00e0y tr\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t l\u00e3ng m\u1ea1n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi b\u1ea1n m\u1eb7c trang ph\u1ee5c c\u01b0\u1edbi. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng ch\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean v\u0169 \u0111i\u1ec7u cho ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh. <span style=\"font-size: 14.4px;\">Trao nhau \u00e1nh m\u1eaft \u0111\u1eafm say c\u00e0ng t\u0103ng th\u00eam s\u1ef1 l\u00e3ng m\u1ea1n cho v\u0169 \u0111i\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang \u0111\u00f4i ta<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cong_nang_tren_lung\"><\/span><strong>C\u00f5ng n\u00e0ng tr\u00ean l\u01b0ng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng ki\u1ec3u s\u00e1nh \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f9ng nhau, t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u1ea3nh c\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u00f5ng n\u00e0ng tr\u00ean l\u01b0ng. T\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i ch\u1ecdn\u00a0t\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh c\u01b0\u1edbi ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi. Phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y s\u1ebd to\u00e1t l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd c\u1ee7a ch\u00e0ng, c\u0169ng ng\u1ea7m kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00e0ng s\u1ebd \u201cc\u00f5ng\u201d n\u00e0ng c\u1ea3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u1eefng g\u00ec khi ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh c\u01b0\u1edbi ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media xem qua m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh cho c\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i s\u1eafp c\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 album \u1ea3nh c\u01b0\u1edbi ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[84,63],"tags":[553],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v18.7 (Yoast SEO v19.9) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh cho c\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i - \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media Digital Marketing<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media xem qua m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ki